86
00:08:23,990 --> 00:08:24,450
That's right.

87
00:08:24,450 --> 00:08:26,200
Can you describe

88
00:08:26,210 --> 00:08:27,740
the entire situation to me?

89
00:08:29,380 --> 00:08:32,030
Back then, I was terrified.

90
00:08:32,740 --> 00:08:35,080
