141
00:10:20,410 --> 00:10:21,940
Did you steal my keys again?

142
00:10:22,640 --> 00:10:23,850
Do you expect me to wait for you

143
00:10:23,850 --> 00:10:25,250
in front of the door then?

144
00:10:44,690 --> 00:10:46,830
Were you hurt?

145
00:10:47,040 --> 00:10:48,680
Lowly thugs like them

146
00:10:48,800 --> 00:10:50,020
can never hurt me.

147
00:10:50,480 --> 00:10:51,680
I'm glad to hear that.

148
00:10:52,080 --> 00:10:53,380
Where did you go after that?

149
00:10:53,380 --> 00:10:55,780
I went back to the mall
to retrieve my stuff.

150
00:10:57,290 --> 00:10:58,290
This is a warning.

151
00:10:58,840 --> 00:11:00,560
You better pick an appropriate time

152
00:11:00,560 --> 00:11:02,420
if you plan to summon me next time.

153
00:11:02,660 --> 00:11:03,670
