154
00:11:03,670 --> 00:11:04,550
if I lose them.

155
00:11:05,140 --> 00:11:06,530
Did you rob a bank?

156
00:11:10,050 --> 00:11:12,150
Are you sure you only pawned
your jade pendant

157
00:11:12,150 --> 00:11:13,080
and didn't rob a bank?

158
00:11:13,080 --> 00:11:15,350
Although I don't mind

159
00:11:15,560 --> 00:11:16,980
messing with the cops here,

160
00:11:16,980 --> 00:11:18,330
I won't attract their attention

161
00:11:18,330 --> 00:11:19,460
under such circumstances

162
00:11:19,460 --> 00:11:20,850
unless it's necessary.

163
00:11:21,390 --> 00:11:22,230
After all,

164
00:11:22,270 --> 00:11:22,860
I don't have

165
00:11:22,860 --> 00:11:24,330
a legal identity in this era yet.

166
00:11:24,330 --> 00:11:26,330
Great. You had me for a moment there.

167
00:11:27,650 --> 00:11:28,110
If so...

168
00:11:28,150 --> 00:11:28,950
Are you trying

169
00:11:28,990 --> 00:11:30,250
to ask me why I appeared

170
00:11:30,420 --> 00:11:31,640
and saved you again?

171
00:11:33,450 --> 00:11:34,780
Let me be clear with you.

172
00:11:35,130 --> 00:11:36,640
I wasn't trying to save you.

173
00:11:36,640 --> 00:11:39,160
I was just keeping an eye on my hostage.

174
00:11:39,750 --> 00:11:40,460
Besides,

175
00:11:40,880 --> 00:11:42,640
when it comes to double-crossing people,

176
00:11:42,640 --> 00:11:43,900
I'm the only one

177
00:11:44,070 --> 00:11:46,070
who can double-cross other people.

178
00:11:46,380 --> 00:11:47,470
So, it was me

179
00:11:47,600 --> 00:11:49,070
who summoned you again?

180
00:11:49,240 --> 00:11:50,920
I remember I told you this before.

181
00:11:50,920 --> 00:11:52,680
I heard your voice

182
00:11:52,850 --> 00:11:54,070
before I was summoned by you.

183
00:11:54,070 --> 00:11:56,420
[Someone, help me.
Stop showing off your relationship.]

184
00:11:56,420 --> 00:11:58,060
[Can someone help me out?]

185
00:11:58,810 --> 00:12:01,000
[Help!]

186
00:12:02,170 --> 00:12:04,100
I heard your voice again this time.

187
00:12:04,480 --> 00:12:07,260
But what's the connection
between the two incidents?

188
00:12:07,260 --> 00:12:08,790
Although the words you said

189
00:12:09,150 --> 00:12:11,200
weren't related,

190
00:12:11,580 --> 00:12:13,300
both situations

191
00:12:13,430 --> 00:12:14,630
were pretty similar.

192
00:12:16,410 --> 00:12:17,630
It happens

193
00:12:18,010 --> 00:12:19,480
whenever you need a hero

194
00:12:19,480 --> 00:12:20,860
to save you.

195
00:12:21,700 --> 00:12:22,880
A hero?

196
00:12:24,270 --> 00:12:25,070
You don't say?

197
00:12:25,650 --> 00:12:27,040
Do you think you can escape unscathed

198
00:12:27,040 --> 00:12:27,920
in both situations

199
00:12:27,920 --> 00:12:29,050
without any help?

200
00:12:31,870 --> 00:12:32,750
[He's the person]

201
00:12:32,750 --> 00:12:34,480
[the fairy had sent to save me.]

202
00:12:35,350 --> 00:12:35,900
[If so, that means]

203
00:12:35,900 --> 00:12:38,100
[I can do whatever I want in the future.]

204
00:12:38,250 --> 00:12:39,470
[I just need to summon him]

205
00:12:39,470 --> 00:12:41,110
[during crucial moments.]

206
00:12:44,090 --> 00:12:44,950
Let me warn you.

207
00:12:45,010 --> 00:12:46,230
You're not allowed

208
00:12:46,400 --> 00:12:48,460
to get into any trouble in the future.

209
00:12:48,670 --> 00:12:50,390
What trouble can I get into?

210
00:12:50,720 --> 00:12:51,690
With a brain like yours,

211
00:12:51,690 --> 00:12:52,450
I wouldn't be surprised

212
00:12:52,450 --> 00:12:53,780
if you get into trouble.

213
00:12:53,790 --> 00:12:55,590
Anyway, I've made myself clear.

214
00:12:55,600 --> 00:12:57,070
If you summon me again,

215
00:12:57,230 --> 00:12:58,030
I will never help you out

216
00:12:58,030 --> 00:12:59,690
no matter what happens to you.

217
00:12:59,800 --> 00:13:00,760
And, if you keep

218
00:13:00,890 --> 00:13:02,230
getting into trouble,

219
00:13:02,360 --> 00:13:03,220
I have no choice

220
00:13:03,280 --> 00:13:05,880
