224
00:13:17,020 --> 00:13:18,320
Cut to the chase.

225
00:13:19,750 --> 00:13:21,480
I will definitely regret this.

226
00:13:22,980 --> 00:13:24,160
Come with me.

227
00:13:29,990 --> 00:13:30,460
Come on.

228
00:13:50,610 --> 00:13:51,410
Come in.

229
00:13:58,220 --> 00:13:59,520
