230
00:13:59,770 --> 00:14:01,240
Of course it's mine.

231
00:14:04,350 --> 00:14:05,940
Let me make things clear.

232
00:14:06,490 --> 00:14:07,150
This is only

233
00:14:07,200 --> 00:14:08,800
a temporary shelter for you.

234
00:14:09,050 --> 00:14:10,980
