235
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:12,120
But only

236
00:14:12,200 --> 00:14:13,170
if you agree to one condition.

237
00:14:13,170 --> 00:14:14,930
What condition?

238
00:14:17,370 --> 00:14:18,080
You cannot

239
00:14:18,290 --> 00:14:19,720
come to find me whenever you like it,

240
00:14:19,720 --> 00:14:20,380
especially

241
00:14:20,430 --> 00:14:21,830
when my mother is around.

242
00:14:21,860 --> 00:14:22,870
If not, I won't be able to explain myself

243
00:14:22,870 --> 00:14:24,330
when she sees us together.

244
00:14:27,360 --> 00:14:28,920
Are you saying

245
00:14:29,090 --> 00:14:31,060
that I need to consider your feelings

246
00:14:31,060 --> 00:14:32,990
and not create any trouble for you?

247
00:14:33,580 --> 00:14:34,380
That's right.

248
00:14:42,150 --> 00:14:43,070
But why must I

249
00:14:43,240 --> 00:14:44,640
consider your feelings?

250
00:14:44,960 --> 00:14:45,510
You!

251
00:14:45,760 --> 00:14:47,290
Did you forget your status?

252
00:14:47,480 --> 00:14:49,120
You're a hostage.

253
00:14:49,450 --> 00:14:51,550
I'm the one who's keeping you hostage.

254
00:14:51,550 --> 00:14:53,880
You don't want your mother
to see me? Fine.

255
00:14:53,910 --> 00:14:55,920
You have to give me something in return.

256
00:14:55,920 --> 00:14:56,930
You're

257
00:14:57,270 --> 00:14:59,200
rotten to the core.

258
00:15:01,760 --> 00:15:02,730
You don't like it?

259
00:15:02,730 --> 00:15:04,730
I can move back to your unit anytime.

260
00:15:05,040 --> 00:15:06,930
Your bed is pretty comfortable anyway.

261
00:15:06,930 --> 00:15:07,980
Wait a minute!

262
00:15:09,610 --> 00:15:11,210
Tell me then.

263
00:15:11,460 --> 00:15:12,390
What do you want?

264
00:15:14,280 --> 00:15:15,410
I need

265
00:15:15,490 --> 00:15:16,710
a smartphone.

266
00:15:17,340 --> 00:15:19,540
