267
00:15:20,700 --> 00:15:22,300
A smartphone

268
00:15:22,590 --> 00:15:24,400
is just like a personal computer.

269
00:15:24,400 --> 00:15:26,290
It has an independent operating space

270
00:15:26,290 --> 00:15:27,510
and its own programs.

271
00:15:27,670 --> 00:15:29,520
Its user can install

272
00:15:29,650 --> 00:15:31,500
software, games, navigation apps,

273
00:15:31,500 --> 00:15:32,550
and all kinds of programs offered by

274
00:15:32,550 --> 00:15:33,430
third-party service providers.

275
00:15:33,430 --> 00:15:35,290
It's a collective term for phones

276
00:15:35,320 --> 00:15:36,790
that can connect to
the Internet wirelessly

277
00:15:36,790 --> 00:15:38,250
through a mobile network.

278
00:15:39,520 --> 00:15:39,920
You...

279
00:15:39,940 --> 00:15:40,740
There's no need to be surprised.

280
00:15:40,740 --> 00:15:42,400
I have a photographic memory.

281
00:15:42,960 --> 00:15:44,140
I think I have

282
00:15:44,350 --> 00:15:45,520
a spare smartphone...

283
00:15:45,520 --> 00:15:46,490
For the time being,

284
00:15:46,490 --> 00:15:47,960
I need to study

285
00:15:48,130 --> 00:15:49,550
how to return to the ancient era.

286
00:15:49,550 --> 00:15:50,770
The information I can get online

287
00:15:50,770 --> 00:15:51,950
is way more than
what I can get from the library.

288
00:15:51,950 --> 00:15:53,380
And, they're updated at a rapid pace.

289
00:15:53,380 --> 00:15:54,430
So, do not bother me

290
00:15:54,430 --> 00:15:55,690
for the time being.

291
00:15:56,740 --> 00:15:57,940
Logically speaking,

292
00:15:58,040 --> 00:15:59,510
you should be responsible

293
00:15:59,720 --> 00:16:00,390
for providing me with

